      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle dC=\Delta dS+\Gamma {\frac {dS^{2}}{2}}+\kappa d\sigma +\theta dt\,}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/18036fdfa4708512ddd20aa7f030febe27dd004e" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.838ex; width:32.751ex; height:5.676ex;" alt="{\displaystyle dC=\Delta dS+\Gamma {\frac {dS^{2}}{2}}+\kappa d\sigma +\theta dt\,}"></span></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<p>where the <a href="/wiki/Greeks_(finance)" title="Greeks (finance)">Greeks</a> <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \Delta }">
