<li>Whaley, Robert. "Risk and Return of the CBOE BuyWrite Monthly Index" <i><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.iijournals.com/JOD/">The Journal of Derivatives</a></i>, (Winter 2002), pp.&#160;35–42.</li>
